('Abrasives', 'abrasives', '{"root":{"type":"root","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"mode":"normal","text":"Browse Abrasives industrial supplies and equipment at Machrio. Professional-grade products with competitive pricing and fast shipping.","type":"text","format":0,"style":"","detail":0,"version":1}],"direction":"ltr","textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr"}}', 1, 1, 'Find high-quality abrasives for cutting, grinding, and polishing. ANSI, OSHA, and EN certified.', '🔧', true, '[{"question":"What types of products are in Abrasives?","answer":"Abrasives include grinding wheels, sandpaper, flap discs, wire brushes, and more. These products are designed for cutting, grinding, sanding, and polishing various materials."},{"question":"How do I choose the right Abrasives products?","answer":"Select abrasives based on the material you are working with, the desired finish, and the specific task. Consider the grit size, type of abrasive, and ensure they meet ANSI, OSHA, and EN standards."},{"question":"Does Machrio offer bulk pricing for Abrasives?","answer":"Yes, Machrio offers competitive bulk pricing for abrasives. Contact our sales team for a quote and to discuss your specific needs."}]', '[{"facetName":"brand","expanded":true},{"facetName":"material","expanded":false}]', 'Abrasives are essential tools in industrial maintenance, repair, and operations, used for cutting, grinding, sanding, and polishing various materials. Machrio offers a wide range of abrasives including grinding wheels, sandpaper, flap discs, and more, suitable for metalworking, woodworking, and general surface preparation. Our products meet ANSI, OSHA, and EN standards, ensuring safety and performance.', '{"metaTitle":"Abrasives | Machrio Industrial Supplies","metaDescription":"Shop high-quality abrasives for cutting, grinding, and polishing. ANSI, OSHA, and EN certified. Bulk pricing available."}', '{"root":{"type":"root","children":[{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Abrasives play a crucial role in MRO by enabling efficient material removal, surface preparation, and finishing. High-quality abrasives reduce downtime and improve productivity, making them a vital part of any maintenance toolkit.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"version":1}}', '2026-03-02T04:14:34.949Z', '2026-03-02T04:18:21.916Z'),
('Adhesives, Sealants and Tape', 'adhesives-sealants-and-tape', '{"root":{"type":"root","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"mode":"normal","text":"Browse Adhesives, Sealants and Tape industrial supplies and equipment at Machrio. Professional-grade products with competitive pricing and fast shipping.","type":"text","format":0,"style":"","detail":0,"version":1}],"direction":"ltr","textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr"}}', 1, 2, 'Find a wide range of adhesives, sealants, and tapes for industrial bonding, sealing, and fastening applications.', '🧴', true, '[{"question":"What types of products are in Adhesives, Sealants and Tape?","answer":"Our Adhesives, Sealants and Tape category includes epoxy, cyanoacrylate, silicone, and polyurethane adhesives, as well as caulks, sealants, and a variety of tapes such as duct, electrical, and masking tapes."},{"question":"How do I choose the right Adhesives, Sealants and Tape products?","answer":"Select the right product by considering the application, substrate, environmental conditions, and required certifications. Consult technical data sheets and consult with our experts for guidance."},{"question":"Does Machrio offer bulk pricing for Adhesives, Sealants and Tape?","answer":"Yes, Machrio offers bulk pricing options for large orders. Contact our sales team for a quote and to discuss your specific requirements."}]', '[{"facetName":"brand","expanded":true},{"facetName":"material","expanded":false}]', 'Machrio''s Adhesives, Sealants and Tape category offers a comprehensive range of bonding, sealing, and fastening solutions. From high-strength adhesives to versatile tapes, our products cater to the needs of manufacturers, contractors, and maintenance professionals across various industries. Whether you need to bond, seal, or protect, our selection ensures durability, reliability, and compliance with industry standards such as ANSI, OSHA, EN, and ISO.', '{"metaTitle":"Adhesives, Sealants and Tape | Machrio Industrial Supplies","metaDescription":"Explore a wide range of adhesives, sealants, and tapes for industrial bonding, sealing, and fastening. Reliable and certified products for all MRO needs."}', '{"root":{"type":"root","children":[{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Adhesives, sealants, and tapes are critical for MRO buyers to ensure the longevity and performance of equipment and structures. These products provide reliable bonding, sealing, and protection, reducing downtime and maintenance costs.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"version":1}}', '2026-03-02T04:14:35.211Z', '2026-03-02T04:18:36.507Z'),
('Cleaning and Janitorial', 'cleaning-and-janitorial', '{"root":{"type":"root","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"mode":"normal","text":"Browse Cleaning and Janitorial industrial supplies and equipment at Machrio. Professional-grade products with competitive pricing and fast shipping.","type":"text","format":0,"style":"","detail":0,"version":1}],"direction":"ltr","textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr"}}', 1, 3, 'Find a wide range of cleaning and janitorial supplies for maintaining a safe and hygienic environment in any facility.', '🧹', true, '[{"question":"What types of products are in Cleaning and Janitorial?","answer":"Our Cleaning and Janitorial category includes a wide range of products such as cleaning chemicals, mops, brooms, vacuums, trash bags, and more. These products are designed to meet the needs of various facilities and industries."},{"question":"How do I choose the right Cleaning and Janitorial products?","answer":"Select the right products by considering the specific needs of your facility, such as the type of surfaces, the level of cleanliness required, and the intended use. Look for products that comply with relevant standards like OSHA, ANSI, and ISO."},{"question":"Does Machrio offer bulk pricing for Cleaning and Janitorial?","answer":"Yes, Machrio offers bulk pricing for many of our cleaning and janitorial products. Contact our sales team for more information on bulk orders and discounts."}]', '[{"facetName":"brand","expanded":true},{"facetName":"material","expanded":false}]', 'Machrio''s Cleaning and Janitorial category offers a comprehensive range of products designed to meet the needs of facility managers and procurement professionals. From industrial cleaning chemicals and equipment to janitorial supplies, our selection ensures that you can maintain a clean, safe, and hygienic environment. Our products are suitable for various applications in industries such as healthcare, manufacturing, and hospitality, and comply with relevant standards like OSHA, ANSI, and ISO.', '{"metaTitle":"Cleaning and Janitorial | Machrio Industrial Supplies","metaDescription":"Shop a wide range of cleaning and janitorial supplies at Machrio. Find high-quality, compliant products for maintaining a clean and hygienic environment."}', '{"root":{"type":"root","children":[{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Effective cleaning and janitorial practices are crucial for MRO buyers to ensure a safe and productive work environment. Machrio provides a broad selection of high-quality, compliant products that support these critical maintenance activities.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"version":1}}', '2026-03-02T04:14:35.501Z', '2026-03-02T04:18:25.015Z'),
('Electrical', 'electrical', '{"root":{"type":"root","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"mode":"normal","text":"Browse Electrical industrial supplies and equipment at Machrio. Professional-grade products with competitive pricing and fast shipping.","type":"text","format":0,"style":"","detail":0,"version":1}],"direction":"ltr","textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr"}}', 1, 4, 'Find a wide range of electrical supplies, from wiring and cabling to circuit breakers and switches, all meeting industry standards.', '⚡', true, '[{"question":"What types of products are in Electrical?","answer":"Our Electrical category includes wiring, cabling, circuit breakers, switches, outlets, and other essential components for power distribution and control systems."},{"question":"How do I choose the right Electrical products?","answer":"Select products based on your specific requirements, such as voltage, amperage, and environmental conditions. Ensure they meet relevant certifications like ANSI, OSHA, EN, and ISO."},{"question":"Does Machrio offer bulk pricing for Electrical?","answer":"Yes, Machrio offers bulk pricing for Electrical products. Contact our sales team for more information and to discuss your specific needs."}]', '[{"facetName":"brand","expanded":true},{"facetName":"material","expanded":false}]', 'Machrio''s Electrical category offers a comprehensive range of products for industrial and commercial applications, including wiring, cabling, circuit breakers, switches, and more. Our selection is designed to meet the needs of facility managers, electricians, and procurement professionals, ensuring reliable and efficient electrical systems. All products adhere to ANSI, OSHA, EN, and ISO standards, providing peace of mind for safety and performance.', '{"metaTitle":"Electrical | Machrio Industrial Supplies","metaDescription":"Shop a wide range of electrical supplies, including wiring, cabling, circuit breakers, and switches, all meeting ANSI, OSHA, EN, and ISO standards."}', '{"root":{"type":"root","children":[{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"For MRO buyers, the Electrical category is crucial for maintaining and upgrading electrical systems. Reliable and certified electrical components ensure smooth operations, reduce downtime, and enhance safety in industrial and commercial settings.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"version":1}}', '2026-03-02T04:14:35.769Z', '2026-03-02T04:18:28.102Z'),
('Fasteners', 'fasteners', '{"root":{"type":"root","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"mode":"normal","text":"Browse Fasteners industrial supplies and equipment at Machrio. Professional-grade products with competitive pricing and fast shipping.","type":"text","format":0,"style":"","detail":0,"version":1}],"direction":"ltr","textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr"}}', 1, 5, 'Explore a wide range of bolts, nuts, screws, and more. Reliable fastening solutions for all your MRO needs.', '🔩', true, '[{"question":"What types of products are in Fasteners?","answer":"The Fasteners category includes bolts, nuts, screws, washers, and other fastening solutions. These products are available in various materials, sizes, and types to suit different applications."},{"question":"How do I choose the right Fasteners products?","answer":"Select fasteners based on the specific requirements of your application, including material, size, and type. Consider environmental factors and ensure the products meet relevant standards such as ANSI, ISO, and EN."},{"question":"Does Machrio offer bulk pricing for Fasteners?","answer":"Yes, Machrio offers bulk pricing for fasteners. Contact our sales team for a quote and to discuss your specific needs and volume discounts."}]', '[{"facetName":"brand","expanded":true},{"facetName":"material","expanded":false}]', 'Machrio''s Fasteners category offers a comprehensive range of bolts, nuts, screws, and other fastening solutions. Designed to meet the needs of industrial, construction, and manufacturing sectors, our selection includes both standard and specialized fasteners, ensuring reliability and durability in various applications. Whether you''re looking for corrosion-resistant options or high-strength fasteners, we provide products that adhere to ANSI, ISO, and other international standards.', '{"metaTitle":"Fasteners | Machrio Industrial Supplies","metaDescription"