('Hydraulics', 'hydraulics', '{"root":{"type":"root","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"mode":"normal","text":"Browse Hydraulics industrial supplies and equipment at Machrio. Professional-grade products with competitive pricing and fast shipping.","type":"text","format":0,"style":"","detail":0,"version":1}],"direction":"ltr","textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr"}}', 1, 10, 'Explore a wide range of hydraulic components, including pumps, cylinders, valves, and fittings, for industrial MRO needs.', '💧', true, '[{"question":"What types of products are in Hydraulics?","answer":"The Hydraulics category includes hydraulic pumps, cylinders, valves, fittings, hoses, and accessories. These components are designed to work together to power and control fluid-based systems."},{"question":"How do I choose the right Hydraulics products?","answer":"Select hydraulics based on your specific application requirements, such as pressure, flow rate, and operating conditions. Refer to industry standards and consult with our experts for guidance."},{"question":"Does Machrio offer bulk pricing for Hydraulics?","answer":"Yes, Machrio offers bulk pricing for hydraulics. Contact our sales team for volume discounts and to discuss your specific needs."}]', '[{"facetName":"brand","expanded":true},{"facetName":"material","expanded":false}]', 'Machrio''s Hydraulics category offers a comprehensive range of products, including hydraulic pumps, cylinders, valves, and fittings. These components are essential for the efficient operation of machinery in various industries, from manufacturing to construction. Our selection caters to the needs of procurement professionals and facility managers, ensuring reliable performance and compliance with industry standards such as ANSI, OSHA, and ISO.', '{"metaTitle":"Hydraulics | Machrio Industrial Supplies","metaDescription":"Shop a wide range of hydraulic components, including pumps, cylinders, valves, and fittings, for reliable industrial MRO solutions."}', '{"root":{"type":"root","children":[{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Hydraulics play a crucial role in the maintenance and operation of industrial equipment. Reliable and efficient hydraulic components ensure smooth operations, reduce downtime, and enhance productivity, making them a vital part of any MRO strategy.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"version":1}}', '2026-03-02T04:14:37.551Z', '2026-03-02T04:18:59.497Z'),
