('Lubrication', 'lubrication', '{"root":{"type":"root","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"mode":"normal","text":"Browse Lubrication industrial supplies and equipment at Machrio. Professional-grade products with competitive pricing and fast shipping.","type":"text","format":0,"style":"","detail":0,"version":1}],"direction":"ltr","textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr"}}', 1, 13, 'Explore a wide range of industrial lubricants, greases, and oils for optimal machinery performance and longevity.', '🛢️', true, '[{"question":"What types of products are in Lubrication?","answer":"Our Lubrication category includes a variety of products such as industrial lubricants, greases, oils, and specialized additives. These products cater to different applications and industries, ensuring optimal performance and durability."},{"question":"How do I choose the right Lubrication products?","answer":"Select the right lubrication products by considering the operating conditions, such as temperature, load, and speed. Check for compatibility with your equipment and ensure the product meets industry standards and certifications like ISO, ANSI, and OSHA."},{"question":"Does Machrio offer bulk pricing for Lubrication?","answer":"Yes, Machrio offers bulk pricing for lubrication products. Contact our sales team for more information on bulk orders and special discounts to meet your large-scale MRO needs."}]', '[{"facetName":"brand","expanded":true},{"facetName":"material","expanded":false}]', 'Machrio''s Lubrication category offers a comprehensive range of products designed to meet the maintenance, repair, and operational needs of industrial facilities. Our selection includes lubricants, greases, oils, and specialized additives suitable for various applications across multiple industries. Whether you need high-temperature resistance, water resistance, or specific viscosity, our products are engineered to enhance equipment performance, reduce wear, and extend machinery life.', '{"metaTitle":"Lubrication | Machrio Industrial Supplies","metaDescription":"Find a wide range of industrial lubricants, greases, and oils at Machrio. Enhance machinery performance and longevity with our high-quality lubrication products"}', '{"root":{"type":"root","children":[{"children":[{"detail":0,"format":0,"mode":"normal","style":"","text":"Effective lubrication is crucial for maintaining the efficiency and longevity of industrial machinery. Properly selected lubricants can significantly reduce downtime, lower maintenance costs, and improve overall operational performance.","type":"text","version":1}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"type":"paragraph","version":1,"textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr","format":"","indent":0,"version":1}}', '2026-03-02T04:14:38.331Z', '2026-03-02T04:19:32.844Z'),
('Machining', 'machining', '{"root":{"type":"root","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","format":"","indent":0,"version":1,"children":[{"mode":"normal","text":"Browse Machining industrial supplies and equipment at Machrio. Professional-grade products with competitive pricing and fast shipping.","type":"text","format":0,"style":"","detail":0,"version":1}],"direction":"ltr","textFormat":0,"textStyle":""}],"direction":"ltr"}}', 1, 14, 'Find high-precision machining tools and equipment for manufacturing, automotive, and aerospace industries at Machrio.', '⚙️', true, '[{"question":"What types of products are in Machining?","answer":"Our Machining category includes CNC machines, lathes, milling machines, drill presses, and other precision tools for cutting, shaping, and finishing materials."},{"question":"How do I choose the right Machining products?","answer":"Consider your specific application, material type, and production volume. Look for products with relevant certifications (e.g., ANSI, ISO) and consult with our experts for tailored recommendations."},{"question":"Does Machrio offer bulk pricing for Machining?","answer":"Yes, Machrio offers competitive bulk pricing for Machining products. Contact our sales team for a custom quote based on your order volume and specific needs."}]', '[{"facetName":"brand","expanded":true},{"facetName":"material","expanded":false}]', 'Machrio''s Machining category offers a comprehensive range of tools and equipment for precision cutting, shaping, and finishing. Our selection includes CNC machines, lathes, milling machines, and more, catering to the needs of manufacturing, automotive, and aerospace industries. Whether you are a small workshop or a large-scale production facility, our high-quality machining solutions ensure efficiency, accuracy, and durability.', '{"metaTitle":"Machining | Machrio Industrial Supplies","metaDescription":"Explore a wide range of high-precision machining tools and equipment for